OL,3,CSt Helier Parish rates tax will rise
OL,4,Cfrom 2025
OL,6,FParish rates in St Helier will
OL,7,Fincrease by 5.6% from 2025.
OL,9,FIt will see around #22 added to the
OL,10,Fyearly tax bill for a three-bed home
OL,11,Fand #6 for a one-bed flat.
OL,13,FThe extra revenue will partly be used
OL,14,Fto fund road improvements and two new
OL,15,Fplaygrounds in Parade Gardens, costing
OL,16,Fa total of #750,000 according to the
OL,17,FParish.
OL,19,FAn initial #490,000 will also be
OL,20,Fringfenced for a neighbourhood scheme
OL,21,Fwhich aims to improve St Helier.
