OL,3,CSt Helier Parish rates tax will rise
OL,4,Cfrom 2025
OL,6,FConstable Simon Crowcroft presented
OL,7,Fthe parish accounts for the coming
OL,8,Fyear to around 60 ratepayers who
OL,9,Fattended a public meeting at the Town
OL,10,FHall.
OL,12,FThose in attendance unanimously agreed
OL,13,Fto the rate rise with the Parish
OL,14,Fstating "a clear expectation that the
OL,15,FGovernment should be
OL,17,Frequired to honour previous promises
OL,18,Fto contribute to the costs of
OL,19,Fimproving St Helier's residential
OL,21,Fareas".
